i'd tell you now if the media wasn't here,'' roemer joked when asked tuesday about his choice by a class of high school students in baton rouge. ``i'll make an announcement in a joint news conference later this week.''
he'll make the announcement thursday morning, i believe at 9 a.m.,'' an aide told reporters
gore also plans a 9 a.m. news conference thursday ``to announce a major statewide endorsement,'' according to his campaign officials
other presidential candidates are planning swings through louisiana prior to the march 8 super tuesday presidential primaries and caucuses in 20 states and american samoa
