c&amp;d commodities, a large investment fund, was a heavy buyer of soybean meal and soybean oil futures but the action attracted little buying interest among other traders, analysts said
the market didn't respond, so we started to sell off and the thing snowballed late in the day,'' said victor lespinasse, a trader for dean witter reynolds inc. ``we ended up near or at the day's lows across the board.''
