other late dollar rates in europe vs. late tuesday included: 1.6945 west german marks, up from 1.6855; 1.4005 swiss francs, up from 1.3915; 5.7345 french francs, up from 5.7065; 1.9013 dutch guilders, up from 1.8940; 1,247 italian lire, up from 1,244.35; 1.2558 canadian dollars, down from 1.2570
